# Advanced context engineering

For tasks that span multiple files, refactors, or ambiguous requirements:

1. Read `docs/context-engineering/advanced-context-engineering/ace-fca.md` before locking in a large plan.
2. Prefer explicit phases: inventory → plan → implement → verify.
3. Keep “why” and constraints in `docs/figma/imports/*/CONTEXT.md` when work is Figma-driven.

Do not paste the entire ACE doc into chat; reference paths only.
